General.Name: Kalleback Property Invest AB
General.Description: Kallebäck Property Invest AB (publ) operates as a real estate company primarily in Sweden. It owns, manages, and leases Kallebäck 17:2, a property that consists of an office building located in Gothenburg. Kallebäck Property Invest AB (publ) was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
